Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • environmentalDataLogging.entities.BaseEntity
      • environmentalDataLogging.entities.User

  • @Entity
public class User
extends BaseEntity
    The user entity class is the link to the user table in the EnviroDB database. A user contains all the information about the a person who works for the Environmental Technologies lab
